results.name: a(n) = A055086(n) - A000005(n).
comment: It appears that the indices of the zeros in the sequence are in A018253. - _Omar E. Pol_, Oct 22 2013
example: n=15: sequence of D1 = {floor(15/j)} = {15,7,5,3,3,2,2,1,1,1,1,1,1,1,1}, Union(D1) = {15,7,5,3,2,1} = divisors(15) and {7,2}, a(15)=2 the number of terms beyond divisors.
